  <section>
   <title>Features</title>
   <ul>
    <li>Non-destructive, non-repetitive configuration management</li>
    <li>pg_ctl interface</li>
    <li>initdb interface</li>
    <li>postgresql.conf configuration management</li>
    <li>pg_hba.conf configuration management</li>
    <li>pg_hba console script for modifying an hba file</li>
    <li>pg_dotconf console script for modifying a configuration file</li>
   </ul>
